text: Dead Reckoning is a 1947 American mystery movie directed by John Cromwell and starring Humphrey Bogart, Lizabeth Scott, Wallace Ford, George Chandler, Morris Carnovsky. It was distributed by Columbia Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1947 mystery movies Category:American mystery movies Category:Movies directed by John Cromwell Category:Columbia Pictures movies
